GONNA DO NOW?

35
00:03:00,333 --> 00:03:01,958
- WELL, ITS NOT GOOD.

36
00:03:03,875 --> 00:03:07,125
- YOU MEAN INTO THE CANYON?!
THEY'RE GONNA DROP THE STEAMER?!

37
00:03:07,208 --> 00:03:09,833
OH MAN, WHY CAN'T
I JUST GET A BREAK?

38
00:03:09,916 --> 00:03:11,666
