TO THE TINIEST SCRIBBLES

63
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:21,166
YOU MUST'VE HAD
A LOT OF RESPECT FOR YOUR DAD.

64
00:04:21,250 --> 00:04:22,916
- Man: KAITE?

65
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,208
KAITE!

66
00:04:25,458 --> 00:04:27,916
KAITE, YOU MUST BECOME
THE KIND OF PERSON

67
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,625
WHO DOES THINGS FOR OTHERS.

68
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,250
AS FOR ME,

69
00:04:32,333 --> 00:04:34,500
I WAS ABLE TO DO IT
WITH THE SAND STEAMER.

70
00:04:34,583 --> 00:04:37,125
I WONDER WHAT YOU'LL DEVOTE
YOUR LIFE TO, MY SON.

71
00:04:41,416 --> 00:04:43,291
- ( crying )

72
