IF THEY PICK IT UP.

102
00:06:18,166 --> 00:06:19,541
- HMM?

103
00:06:19,625 --> 00:06:22,416
- ( panting )

104
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:24,375
HE-- HE GOT US, BOSS.

105
00:06:24,458 --> 00:06:25,958
HE'S NOT HUMAN.

106
00:06:26,041 --> 00:06:27,333
( groans )

107
00:06:33,083 --> 00:06:34,958
- HMM.
( laughing )

108
