THEY'RE GONNA BE?

126
00:07:20,250 --> 00:07:22,958
HUH?
WAIT, ISN'T THIS--

127
00:07:23,041 --> 00:07:25,208
IT'S SIMPLE. ALL YOU HAVE
TO DO IS TALK INTO IT

128
00:07:25,291 --> 00:07:26,791
AND I'LL HEAR YOU.
I DON'T WANT TO BE CAUGHT

129
00:07:26,875 --> 00:07:28,500
IN SOME SHOOTOUT
IN A NARROW PASSAGEWAY,

130
00:07:28,583 --> 00:07:29,958
SO I'M GONNA BE
COUNTING ON YOUR HELP.

131
00:07:30,041 --> 00:07:31,541
DON'T LET ME DOWN, OKAY?

132
00:07:31,625 --> 00:07:34,083
- HMM.
HOLD ON JUST A MINUTE!

133
00:07:34,166 --> 00:07:35,333
WHERE DID YOU GET THIS?

134
00:07:35,416 --> 00:07:36,958
WHAT ARE YOU DOING WITH
THIS LOST TECHNOLOGY?

135
00:07:37,041 --> 00:07:38,708
JUST WHO THE HELL
ARE YOU, ANYWAY?

136
00:07:38,791 --> 00:07:41,458
- I'D EXPLAIN IT TO YOU,
BUT YOU WOULDN'T BELIEVE ME.

137
00:07:41,541 --> 00:07:43,250
BESIDES, THERE'S NO TIME.

138
00:07:43,333 --> 00:07:45,916
DON'T WORRY SO MUCH
ABOUT THE LITTLE DETAILS.

139
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:48,250
SEE YA!
- ( cocks )

140
00:07:48,333 --> 00:07:51,916
- ( gasps )
- ( rapid gunfire )

141
00:07:53,458 --> 00:07:54,958
- ( gasps )

142
00:07:56,458 --> 00:07:57,791
