143
00:07:57,875 --> 00:08:00,541
- NO, KAITE. IT WASN'T
SUPPOSED TO START LIKE THIS.

144
00:08:00,625 --> 00:08:02,708
- I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
WHAT'S WRONG?

145
00:08:02,791 --> 00:08:04,916
- I SCREWED UP.
THEY'RE BLEEDING BADLY.

146
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,458
I HAVE TO HELP THEM.
- HELP THEM?

147
00:08:07,541 --> 00:08:09,791
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

148
00:08:09,875 --> 00:08:12,416
ARE YOU ACTUALLY SAYING
THAT YOU PURPOSEFULLY AVOIDED

149
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:14,375
KILLING THEM THE ENTIRE TIME?

150
00:08:14,458 --> 00:08:16,875
HUH?  WHAT--

151
00:08:16,958 --> 00:08:19,916
WHAT THE HELL?!
I DON'T UNDERSTAND YOU!

152
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,500
NO MATTER HOW GOOD
A SHOT YOU ARE,

153
00:08:21,583 --> 00:08:22,416
UNLESS YOU SHOOT TO KILL,

154
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:24,541
YOU'RE GONNA GET
YOURSELF KILLED!

155
00:08:25,583 --> 00:08:26,541
( gasps )

156
00:08:30,208 --> 00:08:31,166
HUH?

157
00:08:32,916 --> 00:08:34,791
- ( grunts )

158
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,416
WELL, I GUESS IT IS KIND OF
A STUPID APPROACH, ISN'T IT?

159
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:41,083
I KNOW THAT.

160
00:08:41,166 --> 00:08:43,666
- ( gasps )
- YOU'RE RIGHT.

161
00:08:43,750 --> 00:08:46,250
IT IS TRUE.
IT IS VERY SLOPPY OF ME.

162
00:08:48,375 --> 00:08:50,750
BUT YOU KNOW WHAT?
I MADE A PROMISE.

163
00:08:50,833 --> 00:08:53,083
IF I PUT OUT
EVEN ONE FLAME OF LIFE,

164
00:08:53,166 --> 00:08:54,750
