There's something happening

170
00:09:10,791 --> 00:09:12,166
in the central stairway,
third floor!

171
00:09:12,250 --> 00:09:14,291
- GOOD!
PORT PASSENGER CABIN TEAM,

172
00:09:14,375 --> 00:09:16,625
HEAD AROUND BEHIND
THE CENTRAL STAIRWAY QUICKLY!

173
00:09:16,708 --> 00:09:18,833
EVERYBODY ON FLOORS
ONE THROUGH FIVE,

174
00:09:18,916 --> 00:09:21,625
POSITION YOURSELVES AROUND
EACH STAIRWAY AND CLOSE IN NOW.

175
00:09:21,708 --> 00:09:23,333
- WHAT'S OUR TIME?

176
00:09:23,416 --> 00:09:25,041
- SEVEN MINUTES LEFT.

177
00:09:27,666 --> 00:09:29,791
- WHEN YOU GET THERE,
YOU SHOULD SPEED RIGHT ACROSS.

178
00:09:29,875 --> 00:09:31,916
THEY'RE GATHERING ABOVE
AND BELOW YOU RIGHT NOW.

179
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,000
- Vash: Roger.

180
00:09:35,166 --> 00:09:36,125
- ( both grunt )

181
00:09:45,833 --> 00:09:48,875
- THAT'S STUPID.

182
00:09:48,958 --> 00:09:51,833
YOU GOTTA STOP BEING
SO SOFT WITH THOSE BAD LADS!

183
00:09:51,916 --> 00:09:54,666
NO, IT'S MORE THAN THAT!
STOP BEING SO DAMN SOFT

184
00:09:54,750 --> 00:09:57,125
WITH THE ENTIRE HUMAN RACE!
( growls )

185
00:10:16,291 --> 00:10:18,708
I HAVE BETRAYED,
THEY HAVE BETRAYED,

186
00:10:18,791 --> 00:10:21,125
