OF INNOCENT PEOPLE DIE!

187
00:10:21,208 --> 00:10:23,791
IT'S TOO LATE
FOR US TO GO BACK NOW!

188
00:10:23,875 --> 00:10:25,833
AND-- AND YOU'RE
TOO DAMN CLEAN!

189
00:10:25,916 --> 00:10:28,750
