190
00:10:28,833 --> 00:10:30,791
- ( footsteps )
- HUH?

191
00:10:31,958 --> 00:10:33,750
- THEN YOU SHOULD START OVER.

192
00:10:33,833 --> 00:10:35,291
- WHAT?

193
00:10:37,666 --> 00:10:39,125
- THE TICKET TO THE FUTURE...

194
00:10:40,666 --> 00:10:42,916
IS ALWAYS OPEN.

195
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:45,125
- Man on voice tube:
He's broken past the central

196
00:10:45,208 --> 00:10:49,333
engineer's cabin. He is good,
a real tough bastard,

197
00:10:49,416 --> 00:10:51,583
but he's also got
the Devil's luck!

198
00:10:51,666 --> 00:10:55,041
- WHAT SHOULD WE DO, BOSS?

199
00:10:55,125 --> 00:10:58,458
I DON'T BELIEVE THAT LUCK
HAS ANYTHING TO DO WITH THIS.

200
00:10:58,541 --> 00:11:00,750
- ( grunting )
- Good, keep going straight.

201
00:11:00,833 --> 00:11:02,791
There should be a stairway
on your right.

202
00:11:02,875 --> 00:11:04,458
Take it all the way down.

203
00:11:06,791 --> 00:11:09,375
Don't go anywhere else.
That's the only unmanned place.

204
00:11:19,416 --> 00:11:22,291
- WELCOME TO THE PARTY.
OH, YOU ARRIVED JUST IN TIME.

205
00:11:22,375 --> 00:11:25,500
I TRUST THAT MY BRILLIANT
DIRECTIONS WERE CLEAR ENOUGH.

206
00:11:25,583 --> 00:11:29,875
- OH, KAITE, YOU'VE GOT TO GET
OUT OF THAT ROOM IMMEDIATELY.

207
00:11:29,958 --> 00:11:31,833
- ( guitar music playing )

208
00:11:51,833 --> 00:11:53,750
- ( gunfire stops )

209
00:11:58,791 --> 00:12:01,416
- I LIKE THE WAY YOU SPARKLE.
VERY IMPRESSIVE.

210
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:03,166
I'M GLAD
YOU'RE A WORTHY OPPONENT.

211
00:12:03,250 --> 00:12:06,708
ARE YOU NO LONGER
AFRAID OF DYING?

212
00:12:06,791 --> 00:12:09,250
- Man on voice tube: We found
him, Boss! It was the kid.

213
00:12:09,333 --> 00:12:11,166
- ( grunts )

214
00:12:12,291 --> 00:12:14,083
- Get up, you pain in the ass.

215
00:12:14,166 --> 00:12:15,791
You gave us
a lot of trouble.

216
00:12:15,875 --> 00:12:17,000
- ( blows thudding )
- ( Kaite grunting )

217
00:12:17,083 --> 00:12:19,125
- LOOKS LIKE
YOU'RE ALL OUT OF TRICKS.

218
00:12:19,208 --> 00:12:21,583
OH WELL.
IT'S A REAL ACCOMPLISHMENT

219
00:12:21,666 --> 00:12:24,083
