00:12:35,416 --> 00:12:37,500
- THAT'S FAR ENOUGH.

226
00:12:37,583 --> 00:12:39,458
- WHAT ARE YOU TRYING TO PULL?

227
00:12:39,541 --> 00:12:42,416
- I'VE NEVER BEEN PARTICULARLY
FOND OF THIS METHOD,

228
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:44,625
